Bristlecone is a supply chain consulting and system Integration multinational company, founded in 1996, with its headquarters situated at San Jose, California. The company is a part of $16.9 billion multinational Mahindra Group. They have completed more than 300 engagements across 20 different industry verticals till now. The company is ranked among the top 10 supply chain system integrators of 2012 in Gartner's Supply Chain System Integrators survey.
